SHOCKING footage of a taxi accident on North Coast Road on Sunday has emerged. The video, which is not for sensitive viewers, shows the taxi crossing the centre median before smashing into a man waiting on the other side of the road. The taxi also smashes into two parked cars. At least 18 people, including two infants, were injured in the collision.read morehttp://northglennews.co.za/110551/watch-terrifying-footage-north-coast-road-taxi-accident/